# Controls what `gcloud run deploy --source .` uploads to Cloud Build.
# Without this file, gcloud falls back to .gitignore (which does NOT exclude
# node_modules/.next), so the whole frontend would be uploaded. Keep the
# engine, datasets, and backend; drop everything the Docker build ignores.
.git
.gitignore
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/.venv
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
Frontend/saferoute-ai/frontend
Routes
